description: Retrieves a list of user settings.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token used to retrieve the next page of results for this operation.

nested_items.name: userSettings
nested_items.description: The user settings.

nested_items.name: cookieSynchronizationConfiguration
nested_items.description: The configuration that specifies which cookies should be synchronized from the end user's local browser to the remote browser.

nested_items.name: allowlist
nested_items.description: The list of cookie specifications that are allowed to be synchronized to the remote browser.

nested_items.name: domain
nested_items.description: The domain of the cookie.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the cookie.

nested_items.name: path
nested_items.description: The path of the cookie.

nested_items.name: blocklist
nested_items.description: The list of cookie specifications that are blocked from being synchronized to the remote browser.

nested_items.name: domain
nested_items.description: The domain of the cookie.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the cookie.

nested_items.name: path
nested_items.description: The path of the cookie.

nested_items.name: copyAllowed
nested_items.description: Specifies whether the user can copy text from the streaming session to the local device.

nested_items.name: deepLinkAllowed
nested_items.description: Specifies whether the user can use deep links that open automatically when connecting to a session.

nested_items.name: disconnectTimeoutInMinutes
nested_items.description: The amount of time that a streaming session remains active after users disconnect.

nested_items.name: downloadAllowed
nested_items.description: Specifies whether the user can download files from the streaming session to the local device.

nested_items.name: idleDisconnectTimeoutInMinutes
nested_items.description: The amount of time that users can be idle (inactive) before they are disconnected from their streaming session and the disconnect timeout interval begins.

nested_items.name: pasteAllowed
nested_items.description: Specifies whether the user can paste text from the local device to the streaming session.

nested_items.name: printAllowed
nested_items.description: Specifies whether the user can print to the local device.

nested_items.name: toolbarConfiguration
nested_items.description: The configuration of the toolbar. This allows administrators to select the toolbar type and visual mode, set maximum display resolution for sessions, and choose which items are visible to end users during their sessions. If administrators do not modify these settings, end users retain control over their toolbar preferences.

nested_items.name: hiddenToolbarItems
nested_items.description: The list of toolbar items to be hidden.
(string) ---

nested_items.name: maxDisplayResolution
nested_items.description: The maximum display resolution that is allowed for the session.

nested_items.name: toolbarType
nested_items.description: The type of toolbar displayed during the session.

nested_items.name: visualMode
nested_items.description: The visual mode of the toolbar.

nested_items.name: uploadAllowed
nested_items.description: Specifies whether the user can upload files from the local device to the streaming session.

nested_items.name: userSettingsArn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the user settings.
